data.description: Beautiful 4bedroom 2 bath ranch located in beautiful Grand Island Reserve. This 2016 home has upgraded cabinets, tile flooring, quartz countertops, dual vanities in both bathrooms. 2019 exterior professionally painted, front entry and rear lanai were screened. Pavers added to rear of home in 2020 which makes a fantastic gathering area.  Continuous concrete landscape curbing installed around front and side landscaping. Trim and doors repainted in 2019. Very nice spacious home.
